OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Flargely clear evening and night though
OL,7,Fbreezy. Cloud will increase from the
OL,8,Fwest around dawn but conditions are
OL,9,Fexpected to remain dry. Windy over
OL,10,Fhigh ground. Feeling cooler than
OL,11,Frecently.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FDry but increasingly cloudy
OL,14,Fthrough the morning. Some sunshine
OL,15,Fwill break through later, especially
OL,16,Fin the east where it'll be more
OL,17,Fprolonged. Overnight, outbreaks of
OL,18,Flight rain will spread eastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
