OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTurning increasingly unsettled on
OL,7,FTuesday with rain and showers. Dry on
OL,8,FWednesday though clouding over after a
OL,9,Fsunny start. Sunny spells developing
OL,10,Fafter a wet and windy start on
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
